programme.desc: Raju, a sloppy PI, goes to Europe to investigate a divorce case and falls in love with Anjali, who is covertly impersonating her friend. Raju s personal and professional lives collide when he thinks that Anjali is the one whom he is investigating.

programme.title: Chhote Sarkar
programme.desc: Amar gets framed for the murder of his uncle and is apprehended by two undercover police officers. He pretends to be of unsound mind and leveraging this lie, he tries to find out why he was framed and who the real murderer is.

programme.title: 3 DEEWAREIN
programme.desc: A documentary filmmaker Chandrika soughts to capture the prison life of three men sentenced to death. Initially hesitant in trusting Chandrika, the men eventually open up and share their stories with her, which leads to some shocking revelations.

programme.title: Jail
programme.desc: Parag, a corporate worker, lives a happy-go-lucky life. His life is turned upside down when he gets falsely implicated for drug peddling and subsequently imprisoned. Thus begins his battle for acquittal and return to his old life.

programme.title: DOOR KE DARSHAN
